    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到《伊利西昂》！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款发生在碎裂群岛上的合作科幻生存游戏：探索、建造、制作，并直面失控的伊利西昂守卫，决定这座陨落乌托邦的命运。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/08d3ba6c989cfc8fb82433c9345f26a9.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/8d86d687fdbdd37747eeb0fdd3297d99.poster.avif?t=1763475498\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/8d86d687fdbdd37747eeb0fdd3297d99.webm?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/8d86d687fdbdd37747eeb0fdd3297d99.mp4?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/c933712007f2170a331ea58d7dec070f.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唤醒沉睡的高塔与尘封终端，重连桥梁、运输线路与整座区块。每一座设施恢复运转，都会改变岛屿格局——也让你更接近重建昔日荣光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/ab0e00b5861b53c9302d2e554de5ad88.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/47da18c209623a6859ccb5be1e09b9db.poster.avif?t=1763475498\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/47da18c209623a6859ccb5be1e09b9db.webm?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/47da18c209623a6859ccb5be1e09b9db.mp4?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/c933712007f2170a331ea58d7dec070f.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能量的回流引来两大威胁：失控的伊利西昂守卫，以及受“伊利西矿石”辐射而异变的野生生物。读懂攻击节奏，灵活闪避，再用手中一切火力反击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/a691f283112d966b558247aab314ffea.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/4e84095b4663219362b5dcec6d493cfe.poster.avif?t=1763475498\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/4e84095b4663219362b5dcec6d493cfe.webm?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/4e84095b4663219362b5dcec6d493cfe.mp4?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/c933712007f2170a331ea58d7dec070f.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >河畔、悬崖或密林深处——先选一块心仪之地，从木质墙体、地板和斜坡搭起简易营地；随后加固、扩张，将其进化为能抵御岛屿狂潮的前线要塞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/e98e9742b4ff66dfd6123d32fdbc8aca.webp?t=1763475498\" width=619 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/5527b4916c29286e880caf1076de1876.poster.avif?t=1763475498\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/5527b4916c29286e880caf1076de1876.webm?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/5527b4916c29286e880caf1076de1876.mp4?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/c933712007f2170a331ea58d7dec070f.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每条路径都通向值得探索的目标：从天文观测站到治愈神龛，各个地标提供新材料、捷径，或伊利西昂文明的历史碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/4f75bf3961005e65b8bab474c82a0705.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/b814d9bd2d0a0cdfb925c6e05167533a.poster.avif?t=1763475498\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/b814d9bd2d0a0cdfb925c6e05167533a.webm?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/b814d9bd2d0a0cdfb925c6e05167533a.mp4?t=1763475498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354810/extras/c933712007f2170a331ea58d7dec070f.webp?t=1763475498\" width=615 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着古老系统逐一重启，诡异模式浮出水面：封闭的大门抗拒开启，高塔触发自动防御，守卫则以难以预测的节奏行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经主宰此地的核心智能依旧注视着一切，潜伏在岛屿骨骼之间，抵抗你迈出的每一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它是在守护残存的文明……还是在掩盖失控的真相？唯有你能揭晓。<br><br><strong>将《伊利西昂》加入愿望单，第一时间见证岛屿苏醒！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿正在觉醒——不要错过它睁眼的瞬间。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 土耳其语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 阿拉伯语, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 瑞典语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 繁体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
